---
// SoftSkillsMindset.astro
---

<section id="mindset" class="ss-section">
  <div class="ss-container">
    <div class="ss-section-header ss-reveal">
      <span class="ss-section-num">01</span>
      <h2 class="ss-section-title">Mindset</h2>
      <p class="ss-section-desc">The internal architecture behind every decision and every line of code.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="ss-mindset-grid">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="ss-mindset-card ss-reveal" style="animation-delay:0.1s">
        <div class="ss-card-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
            <path d="M12 8v4l3 3"/>
            <path d="M12 2a10 10 0 0 1 0 20"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="ss-card-content">
          <h3 class="ss-card-title">Curiosity-driven learning</h3>
          <p class="ss-card-text">
            I don't learn because it's required. I learn because something pulls me in — a system I don't understand, a concept that feels incomplete, a question I can't let go of.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="ss-card-accent"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="ss-mindset-card ss-reveal" style="animation-delay:0.2s">
        <div class="ss-card-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M3 3h7v7H3zM14 3h7v7h-7zM14 14h7v7h-7zM3 14h7v7H3z"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="ss-card-content">
          <h3 class="ss-card-title">Systems thinking</h3>
          <p class="ss-card-text">
            Every problem has a structure. I try to find the root before touching the surface — understanding how pieces connect before deciding which one to move.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="ss-card-accent"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="ss-mindset-card ss-reveal" style="animation-delay:0.3s">
        <div class="ss-card-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="ss-card-content">
          <h3 class="ss-card-title">Growth-focused mentality</h3>
          <p class="ss-card-text">
            Failure is part of the vocabulary. Each dead-end is data — what doesn't work is just as valuable as what does. The direction is always forward, even when the path loops.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="ss-card-accent"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .ss-mindset-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .ss-mindset-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }

  .ss-mindset-card {
    position: relative;
    padding: 36px 32px;
    background: rgba(255, 252, 245, 0.7);
    border: 1px solid rgba(197, 168, 128, 0.2);
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: all 0.35s ease;
    cursor: default;
  }

  .ss-mindset-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    border-color: rgba(197, 168, 128, 0.45);
    box-shadow: 0 16px 48px rgba(120, 80, 30, 0.10);
  }

  .ss-mindset-card:hover .ss-card-accent {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  .ss-card-icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: #c5a880;
  }

  .ss-card-icon svg {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .ss-card-title {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #2c1f10;
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .ss-card-text {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #6b4c2a;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .ss-card-accent {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #c5a880, #e8c89a, transparent);
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(2px);
    transition: all 0.35s ease;
    border-radius: 0 0 0 0;
  }
</style>
